caption:
Ringo

Name: Ringo

Age: 16 Year Old (10th Grade)

Sex: Female

Birthdate: Aquarius/February  


Ringo is very social and energetic. She is the oldest Twin. She like the color green. They’re honest and they can talk for hours if you let them. Plus, they have some pretty interesting opinions and ideas, that will leave you thinking. Honestly, these fellas don’t know when to stop. They don’t know when to stop talking, they don’t know when to show some more decency, they don’t know when lies are more appropriate then the truth. And they may hurt or annoy others.
